==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Howsoever
<hw>How`so*ev"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adj. & conj.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>How</ets> + <ets>so</ets> + <ets>ever</ets>.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>In what manner soever; to whatever degree or extent;
however.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I am glad he's come, <qex>howsoever</qex> he comes.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Although; though; however.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Howve</ent>⟦br⟧
